// How to save the data on local storage.

'Local storage gives an API, and browser has API to directly access this and All of the JS has an access to this one.'
'If we just write localStorage in the fxn, then LocalStorage API will be invoked '

'SetItem: it takes as key, value pairs: key can be any type but value should always be string'

'JSON: Two types, Parse & Stringify', 'Stringify converts into string' & 'Parse: Parse it back from string to its whatever the original data type was.'